rly on, and thereafter decrease with time.\nFor SNe in a constant density medium, the emission would be expected to\nincrease with time upto the advent of the Sedov stage.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Nov 2014 21:07:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Sep 2015 00:22:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-07"}
