de with a brief discussion of open questions. A manuscript\ncontaining more details and full proofs is forthcoming.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Nov 2014 04:06:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Dec 2014 01:32:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-07"}
