work. These results significantly increase the biological plausibility of\nthe spike-based approach to network computation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Nov 2014 15:47:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Jul 2015 16:49:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-17"}
